Rating: 4
Made this for my mother's birthday and it was a hit. She's not a big fan on anything too sugary and this recipe was perfect. Not too sweet, lighter than a cheesecake, and if you spend the extra money on the vanilla beans, it makes a big difference. Didn't change a thing, except that I made it into one big tarte. My graham cracker crust was falling apart a little, so next time I might add a little bit more butter or bake it longer. Other than that, it was a perfect treat!

