Rating: 4
This was great! Following the suggestion of another reviewer, I doubled the ingredients for the cheesecake portion. I used 1/2 regular cream cheese and 1/2 lowfat cream cheese & the filling came out wonderfully smooth and tasty. I also, used 6-tbsp more of the vodka (again I cheated & used Stolichnaya Vanil instead of putzing about with making my own). I also, decided against using vanilla bean in the filling, since the pods are pricey. Instead, I plopped in about 1-tsp of vanilla extract into the filling. If you decide to make this, definitely don't forget the berries & vodka flavoring. The berry/vodka compote will have people begging for another slice. Needless to say, I didn't have any leftovers & the springform pan was licked clean. Cheers!!

